@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_fwnarm(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.sin((0.64 + wp.abs(v1 + 0.17)))
    v2 = (0.37 / v2)
    v1 = (wp.sin(0.03) / (wp.exp(v0 + 0.86) + v2))
    v0 = ((wp.exp(tmp + 0.32) + wp.sin(v1 + 0.90)) * tmp)
    v0 = (wp.exp((v0 + 0.49 + v2 + 0.88)) - ((tmp + 0.21 * tmp + 0.29) * (v0 + 0.03 * tmp + 0.58)))
    v0 = (v2 / (wp.sin(v1 + 0.27) / 0.58))
    v0 = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
